{"tid":1356670,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"727=反白色恐怖，728=五大訴求","createTime":"2019-07-23T14:25:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T15:48:34.000Z","uid":108305,"like":21,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"3f93107bcf7f6ba604a43dd15c6c72a8e8dbe2d7","tid":1356670,"uid":108305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T14:25:33.000Z","msg":"而家何君堯淡氣已經出左，請慢慢等件事丟淡，focus返落36槍先，否則就會focus shifted<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n727元朗遊行 (建議和理非)<br />\n但唔代表我地唔洗去元朗 因為要用和平遊行表達我地唔怕任何恐嚇 並且建立新界居民繼續參與政治既信心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我建議要<span style=\"color: red;\">和理非</span>原因有三:<br />\n一, 用和平對抗暴力 順勢搶佔輿論;<br />\n二, 武力不足以同鄉黑打 避免無謂犧牲 (但請前線上gear自衛);<br />\n三, 避免誤墮政府群眾鬥群眾既策略<br />\n<br />\n728 港島/九龍遊行 (自行決定 但都係建議前線休息一星期)<br />\n見有post手足講有市民未必夠膽入元朗，但呢批人都係會想出黎 甚至會又有新既支持者出黎反鄉黑同警黑合作 所以呢個遊行就係for呢班人 加一貫星期日會出黎既人<br />\n<br />\n我冇權叫前線唔衝 所以我會<span style=\"color: red;\">建議手足自行決定</span> 但我都係希望會抖返一星期先 因為:<br />\n一，暫時唔好再俾差佬有藉口升級武力，因為太多手足有傷在身;<br />\n二, 暫時唔好俾機會差佬翻身 (而家普遍人都好唔妥差佬唔保護市民 淺藍黃絲都係 但如前線又勇武 警察又會捉前線 然後吹返佢執法保護市民生命財產有力 然後又會動搖遊離群組)<br />\n三, 唔再俾機會政府黑警字頭以警力不足做藉口 聯手係其他區搞大龍鳳<br />\n<br />\n利申: 個人愚見 但不論同意與否都多可多加討論 幫手推下post叫人呢兩日出黎都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ab68019a904775664d9dfd07106e528b055eb13","tid":1356670,"uid":108305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T14:27:22.000Z","msg":"傻仔自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"697ec58c847d1a6e111fb7be6fc8a602afe964dc","tid":1356670,"uid":108305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T14:29:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae9349cf763c8cf6aeb7238d6a5d599c4d8d4b73","tid":1356670,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T14:29:15.000Z","msg":"728不如試下真正嘅遍地開花<br />\n而家好開地區都有tg group<br />\n試下搞到狗疲於奔命？"},{"pid":"690fa6f2474e96f6fa47d4c80723e161186cf778","tid":1356670,"uid":19300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T14:29:48.000Z","msg":"光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"375c4463930336b9b423820f1bbee514e95cbbcf","tid":1356670,"uid":237077,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T14:30:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7nBtCFX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7nBtCFX.jpg&h=a3d5aa01&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c80ac05b7b9ff05f2d8aef54cb7fc6f122f3b802","tid":1356670,"uid":108305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae9349cf763c8cf6aeb7238d6a5d599c4d8d4b73","tid":1356670,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T14:29:15.000Z","msg":"728不如試下真正嘅遍地開花<br />\n而家好開地區都有tg group<br />\n試下搞到狗疲於奔命？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T14:31:55.000Z","msg":"遍地開花好事來 應該要做的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但近期風頭火勢 有機會會好似我上面講 又俾政府以警力分薄為由 任由黑勢力係各區開花運動搞事<br />\n而且我地人數分薄都會對手足有危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2638e30997e8e491edc8104b4040cc2863dfd5ef","tid":1356670,"uid":122676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T14:31:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c274148b043063d1d2692807798a945fe815f613","tid":1356670,"uid":264857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T14:32:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"00eb202605a32f360ca93db93b4666f4182ad563","tid":1356670,"uid":99243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T14:32:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f405be7df951ae48bcfefd625e88779bffcadfcc","tid":1356670,"uid":270047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T14:33:28.000Z","msg":"推! 快啲返返黎 727!"},{"pid":"abd3ef235028a229d490fa76588fc9ab970